Description

OmeroRawClient

OmeroRawExtension
Extension to access images hosted on OMERO.
OmeroRawImageServer
ImageServer that reads pixels using the OMERO-JAVA gateway
OmeroRawImageServerBrowserCommand
Command to browse a specified OMERO server and import images from that server
OmeroRawImageServerBuilder
Builder for ImageServers that make use of the OMERO-java library.
OmeroRawImportAnnotationObjectsCommand
Import ROIs from OMERO for the current open image.
OmeroRawImportChannelSettingsCommand
Import channel rendering settings from OMERO.
OmeroRawImportMetadataCommand
Import key-values and tags from OMERO with a certain rule - Keep existing and add new => only add in QuPath the new keys (if the key already exists, it is not imported) - Replace existing and add new => add news keys and update those which already exist (i.e.replace the old value) - Delete all and add new => delete all keys in QuPath and all those coming from OMERO.
OmeroRawScripting
Static class which groups the methods of the scripting API for an OMERORawImageServer
OmeroRawShapes
Handles the conversion between PathObjects and OMERO-ROIs
OmeroRawTools
Static helper methods related to OMERORawImageServer.
OmeroRawWriteAnnotationObjectsCommand
Command to write path objects back to the OMERO server where the current image is hosted.
OmeroRawWriteChannelSettingsCommand
Command to send QuPath channel settings (display range, colors and name) to the corresponding image on OMERO
OmeroRawWriteMetadataCommand
Command to import QuPath metadata to OMERO server where the current image is hosted.
Utils
Utils class regrouping tools that are not restricted to OMERO.
